n apartments swifton ar multifamily program lower your bill with free products from entergy from light bulbs to showerheads the entergy arkansas multifamily program will install energysaving products at no cost to owners or tenants energy efficiency upgrades will add value to your property by lowering water and sewer costs as well as lowering energy costs for tenants entergy arkansas will install these free energysaving products in eligible multifamily properties whats offered in this program  this program is designed to benefit both the property managerowner and tenants the energy efficiency upgrades add value to the property help lower water and sewer costs and provide tenants with decreased energy costs this program also offers both direct installation of costeffective efficiency measures in tenants units as well as common area energy surveys to identify opportunities for future energyefficient improvements and other entergy arkansas energy efficiency programs services include direct installation of compact fluorescent bulbs in tenants residences at no direct cost to the resident direct installation of highefficiency showerheads if there is electric water heating at no direct cost to the tenant direct installation of highefficiency kitchen and bath aerators if there is electric water heating at no direct cost to the tenant air conditioning tuneup performed by a certified technician to clean your system and adjust the refrigerant charge common area energy efficiency analysis report mailed to the property managerowner air conditioning tuneups  the air conditioning tuneup helps each homes system to run more efficiently and provides better comfort to residents while lowering energy costs this is achieved by a certified technician cleaning your system and adjusting refrigerant charge for information on participating contractors click here compact fluorescent light bulbs  most cfls last 0 times longer and use  percent less energy than traditional bulbs entergy will install cfls in fixtures or table lamps in each unit that means less time changing light bulbs and more time saving money on your entergy bill energyefficient showerheads  the showerheads use  percent less water than standard showerheads that means less energy used to heat water for showers additionally these selfcleaning showerheads will not corrode and require zero maintenance entergy will replace all eligible showerheads with these showerheads kitchen  bathroom faucet aerators  entergy will install energyefficient faucet aerators in kitchens and bathrooms made of longlasting materials the aerators use approximately  percent less water than a standard faucet that means less energy used for water heating savings will vary with efficiency of water heating system temperature of incoming and outgoing water and the number of occupants in the home energy survey  an entergy arkansasqualified field technician will perform an energy survey of your propertys common areas at no cost this will identify ways to improve your propertys energy efficiency at the end of the survey the technician will provide you with a summary of recommendations dont wait to save click here to download the complete program manual contact the entergy arkansas multifamily program by email or phone at 666   privacy policy  terms  conditions a message from entergy arkansas inc  04 entergy services inc all rights reserved the entergy solutions program is an energy efficiency program and not affiliated with entergy solutions llc   entergy corporation all rights reserved the entergy name and logo are registered service marks of entergy corporation and may not be used without the express written consent of entergy corporation entergy arkansas inc  energy efficiency download our app myaccount login    newsroom    careers    faq    sitemap    contact us entergy arkansas inc myaccountpayment optionsresidential main pagebusiness main pageour communitybusiness  economic developmentenergy education  safetyabout use