 energy solutions instant incentives longterm savings entergy rewards its agribusiness customers for installing energyefficient measures the goal of the entergy arkansas agricultural energy solutions program is to produce longterm electricity cost savings for agribusinesses by installing energy efficiency measures and replacing aging inefficient equipment eligible businesses have two options for participating in the program  prescriptive lighting this option consists of a series of choices with predetermined incentives for a wide selection of common energyefficient lighting measures including compact fluorescent light bulbs highperformance linear fluorescent replacements pulsestart metal halide lighting controls including occupancy sensors  custom energyefficient technology this option offers incentives for more complex sitespecific and costeffective opportunities for energyefficient technologies custom projects must be able to show specific and verifiable energy savings and costs typical custom measures include lowenergy livestock waterers exhaust fans circulation fans highvolume lowspeed fans milk precooler variable speed controllers for vacuum pumps variable frequency drives program incentives  savings the program provides financial incentives and technical assistance to help agribusinesses replace aging inefficient equipment and systems with new energyefficient technologies prescriptive rebate offering provides a simple method to make efficient choices by offering predetermined incentives for a wide selection of common energyefficient lighting measures such as compact fluorescent bulbs custom rebate offering incentives for more complex and sitespecific opportunities for energyefficient technologies or multimeasure projects that are not included in the prescriptive offerings typical custom measures include exhaust fans variable frequency drives new construction lighting and circulation fans how does my business benefit from this program  an energyefficient facility not only means a lower energy bill for your business but also improved employee comfort and productivity by providing incentives and assistance to agribusinesses that are replacing inefficient equipment entergy helps reduce upfront improvement costs as well as longterm energy bills plus entergy allows customers to engage their own qualified contractors or inhouse staff for improvements who is eligible  the entergy arkansas agricultural energy solutions program is available to all nonresidential electric customers on the following agriculture rate schedules agricultural pumping general farm service small general service large general service this program extends to a variety of agribusiness including poultry dairy cattle swine deltarow crops and aquaculture facilities start saving today click here to download the complete program manual learn more about the agricultural energy solutions program and how it can benefit your business contact program account manager cody allen by email or by telephone at 040 to get started today please note an applicant considered a free rider will be disqualified from program participation a free rider is someone who would install an energy efficiency measure without any program incentives or intervention   privacy policy  terms  conditions a message from entergy arkansas inc  04 entergy services inc all rights reserved the entergy solutions program is an energy efficiency program and not affiliated with entergy solutions llc   entergy corporation all rights reserved the entergy name and logo are registered service marks of entergy corporation and may not be used without the express written consent of entergy corporation entergy arkansas electrician  little rock ar projects photos reviews and more  porchzfbzcuyqsybrvyararsyawfcfawwursrfind professionalspopular professionals • see allpaintershandymenplumberselectricianshvac contractorsremodeling contractorsgeneral contractorsrooferscarpentersflooring contractorslandscaperspest control